             sworn. - I am a constable; I searched the prisoner, and found a great number of duplicates; two of them of curtains. - (Produces them.)</p>
               <p>Hyam. These are my duplicates.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I leave it to the mercy of the Jury.</p>
